{
  "chapter": 160,
  "chapter_summary": "第160章\"晚宴风云\"讲述秦国宴会上的一场精心策划的比武。太子丹以犀利言辞暗讽吕不韦想借管中邪立威，吕不韦顺势派出管中邪出战。燕国剑手阎独以燕翔剑法迎战管中邪，但被管中邪击败，额头留下剑痕。吕不韦一方借机挑衅，蔡泽提议让项少龙出战。项少龙明知吕不韦意在当众折辱自己，仍毅然应战。他揭穿管中邪一直隐藏左手剑法的秘密，先声夺人，再以墨子剑法的\"以守代攻\"和\"攻守兼资\"两大杀招与管中邪激战。项少龙以命搏命的打法逼退管中邪七步，吕不韦惊惶喊停。全场为项少龙的豪气和剑术疯狂喝彩。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_zi_dan",
      "speaker_name": "太子丹",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "听说贵府管中邪先生曾大发神威，连败齐国高手，不知今趟是否又派他出来逞显威风？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_tai_zi_dan",
      "text": "得丹太子如此夸赏，中邪愧不敢当，岂能不从尊意，请太子派出贵国高手，让我们一开眼界。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此人是燕国最有名气的三大剑手之一，我们一直不知他随太子丹来咸阳，据说他的燕翔剑快如闪电，可斩杀急飞的燕子，你说多么本事。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位比武，乃友好间的切磋交流，点到即止，切勿让寡人见到伤亡流血的场面。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_yan_du",
      "text": "不用甲冑，阎兄请自便。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_yan_du",
      "text": "管某剑名'长击'，乃出自越国名匠所铸，剑长五尺四寸，比一般剑长上一尺有多，阎兄莫要轻忽它的长度。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "中邪你违反储君吩咐，剑下见血，理该罚你一杯。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cai_ze",
      "speaker_name": "蔡泽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中邪的剑法把我们的兴头引出来，不知昨晚大展神威的荆副统领何在，可否让我们看看谁高谁低？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cai_ze",
      "text": "副统领有任务在身，未能出席，要教蔡大人失望了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cai_ze",
      "speaker_name": "蔡泽",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨晚不是有位桓齮连胜三场吗？就让我们再看看他的本领吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他们在针对你呢！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "管大人既这么有兴致，让我来陪你玩上两招吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人切勿不顾腿伤强行出手，否则末将怎担当得起。",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙万勿勉强！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "若管大人可令我伤口复裂，算我输了吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刀剑无眼，两位卿家小心。",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可与项大人一较高下，是中邪平生快事。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "未知管大人今趟会否使出看家的左手剑法？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人的眼力确是非凡。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "停战！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 160,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    }
  ],
